---

<PageLayout>
    <h1 class="p-20 text-center text-white">
        Benicia Middle School<br>
        Parent Teacher Organization
    </h1>

    <div class="flex gap-10">
        <div>
            <h2>Volunteer!</h2>
            <p>We are still looking for help. We have a couple positions still open on the board. But, we have all sorts of ways you can help.</p>
            <a href="https://forms.gle/Dz7rApxM4kJx9M8fA" class="btn">Volunteer Today!</a>
        </div>

        <div>
            <h2>News</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Read more in the <a href="https://bms.beniciaunified.org/our-school/viking-times-newsletter/">Viking Times</a></li>
